description:
NbIoT Cell configuration parameters from Ericsson's RAN.

- dateTime: Timestamp of the data record.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the cell is located.
- CellId: Unique identifier for the NB-IoT cell.
- Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
- Id3: Alternative/internal identifier for the NB-IoT cell.
- vsDataType: Data type identifier.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
- NbIotCell.attachWithoutPDNConnectivityList: Flag indicating whether attachments without PDN connectivity are allowed.
- NbIotCell.npbchRrmConfigEnabled: Flag indicating whether NPBCCH RRM configuration is enabled.
- NbIotCell.mappingInfo: Mapping information (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.plmnAlarmSupprList: Flag indicating whether PLMN alarm suppression is enabled.
- NbIotCell.physicalLayerCellId: Physical layer cell ID.
- NbIotCell.rachPreambleTransMaxNb: Maximum number of RACH preamble transmissions.
- NbIotCell.additionalSpectrumEmissionValues: Additional spectrum emission values (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.cellBarred: Status of cell barring.
- NbIotCell.periodicBsrTimerDedicated: Timer for periodic buffer status reports (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.enableMfbi: Flag indicating whether MFBI is enabled.
- NbIotCell.qHyst: Hysteresis value for quality.
- NbIotCell.sInterSearchThreshold: Threshold for inter-cell search.
- NbIotCell.nbIotCellType: Type of NB-IoT cell.
- NbIotCell.nbIotCellCoverage: NB-IoT cell coverage information (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.preambleIniRecTargetPowerCe1: Target power for preamble initial reception (CE1).
- NbIotCell.freqBand: Frequency band.
- NbIotCell.maxRrcConnectedUsers: Maximum number of RRC connected users.
- NbIotCell.rlcStatusPduDelayDl: Downlink RLC status PDU delay.
- NbIotCell.tTatDedicatedNbCe2: Dedicated TTI assignment time (CE2).
- NbIotCell.preambleIniRecTargetPowerR14: Target power for preamble initial reception (Rel-14).
- NbIotCell.nbIotCellPolygon: Polygon defining the cell coverage area (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.abContConfFromLastProfile: Flag indicating whether AB continuous configuration is from the last profile.
- NbIotCell.rsrpThreshold2: Second RSRP threshold.
- NbIotCell.ulNonAnchPrbIndex: Uplink non-anchor PRB index (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.maxNumPreambleAttemptNbCe1: Maximum number of preamble attempts (CE1).
- NbIotCell.rsrpThreshold1: First RSRP threshold.
- NbIotCell.maxNumPreambleAttemptNbCe2: Maximum number of preamble attempts (CE2).
- NbIotCell.ulAnchPrbIndex: Uplink anchor PRB index.
- NbIotCell.minNumLargeRmaxUes: Minimum number of large Rmax UEs.
- NbIotCell.pZeroNominalNPusch: Nominal power for NPUSCH.
- NbIotCell.maxNumPreambleAttemptNbCe0: Maximum number of preamble attempts (CE0).
- NbIotCell.nbIotDynOverloadUlNonAnchThr: Uplink non-anchor overload threshold.
- NbIotCell.dlAnchPrbUtilThr: Downlink anchor PRB utilization threshold.
- NbIotCell.operationalState: Operational state of the cell.
- NbIotCell.tRrcConnReest: RRC connection re-establishment timer.
- NbIotCell.abConfProfileRef: Reference to AB configuration profile (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.latitude: Latitude of the cell.
- NbIotCell.dlNonAnchPrbUtilThr: Downlink non-anchor PRB utilization threshold.
- NbIotCell.ulNonAnchPrbUtilThr: Uplink non-anchor PRB utilization threshold.
- NbIotCell.primaryFreqBand: Primary frequency band (likely -1 indicates it's not primary).
- NbIotCell.abMinIntensityThreshold: Minimum intensity threshold for AB.
- NbIotCell.plmnIdList: List of PLMN IDs (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.nprachCapMode4RxEnabled: Flag indicating whether NPRACH capability mode 4RX is enabled.
- NbIotCell.nprachSubcarrierForStMsg3Ce2: Subcarrier allocation for ST Msg3 (CE2).
- NbIotCell.cmcIndex: CMC index.
- NbIotCell.nprachSubcarrierForStMsg3Ce1: Subcarrier allocation for ST Msg3 (CE1).
- NbIotCell.nprachSubcarrierForStMsg3Ce0: Subcarrier allocation for ST Msg3 (CE0).
- NbIotCell.spectrumEmissionReqMapping: Spectrum emission request mapping (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.earfcndl: Downlink EARFCN.
- NbIotCell.dlNonAnchPrbIndex: Downlink non-anchor PRB index (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.intraFrequencyInfo: Intra-frequency information (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.nsssRrmConfigInterFreq: Inter-frequency NSSS RRM configuration (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.anchPowerBoostGainIndex: Anchor power boost gain index.
- NbIotCell.sIntraSearchThreshold: Threshold for intra-cell search.
- NbIotCell.nbIotDynOverloadDlAnchThr: Downlink anchor overload threshold.
- NbIotCell.inactivitySupervisionTimer: Inactivity supervision timer (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.earfcnul: Uplink EARFCN.
- NbIotCell.dlLaIpnAbsolute: Downlink LA-IPN absolute value.
- NbIotCell.enhancedRaPowerCtrl: Flag indicating whether enhanced RA power control is enabled.
- NbIotCell.sectorCarrierRef: Reference to the sector carrier.
- NbIotCell.raBackoffNbCe2: RA backoff for CE2.
- NbIotCell.raBackoffNbCe1: RA backoff for CE1.
- NbIotCell.raiEnabled: Flag indicating whether RAI is enabled.
- NbIotCell.raBackoffNbCe0: RA backoff for CE0.
- NbIotCell.plmnReservedList: Flag indicating whether PLMN reserved list is enabled.
- NbIotCell.abThreshTimeHigh: High threshold time for AB.
- NbIotCell.nbIotAcPresence: NB-IoT AC presence status.
- NbIotCell.nbIotCellId: NB-IoT cell ID.
- NbIotCell.activePlmnList: List of active PLMNs (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.cellRange: Cell range.
- NbIotCell.administrativeState: Administrative state of the cell.
- NbIotCell.frequencyInfo: Frequency information (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.tac: Tracking area code (TAC).
- NbIotCell.raDlSinrAdjustCe: Downlink SINR adjustment for RA (CE).
- NbIotCell.msg3CqiAdjustFactorCe: CQI adjustment factor for Msg3 (CE).
- NbIotCell.siWindowLength: SI window length.
- NbIotCell.longitude: Longitude of the cell.
- NbIotCell.abThreshRejectLow: Low threshold for AB rejection.
- NbIotCell.dlNonAnchPrbNum: Number of downlink non-anchor PRBs.
- NbIotCell.nbDlSinrAdjust: Downlink SINR adjustment for NB-IoT.
- NbIotCell.enhancedPhr: Flag indicating whether enhanced PHR is enabled.
- NbIotCell.cellId: Cell ID.
- NbIotCell.nbIotDynOverloadDlNonAnchThr: Downlink non-anchor overload threshold.
- NbIotCell.sIntraSearchDeltaP: Delta P for intra-cell search.
- NbIotCell.networkSignallingValue: Network signalling value.
- NbIotCell.additionalFreqBandList: List of additional frequency bands (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.npuschGroupHopConfig: NPUSCH group hop configuration.
- NbIotCell.ulAnchPrbUtilThr: Uplink anchor PRB utilization threshold.
- NbIotCell.useHostCellPci: Flag indicating whether host cell PCI is used.
- NbIotCell.cDrxEnabled: Flag indicating whether CD-RX is enabled (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.largeRmaxUeAnchThr: Anchor threshold for large Rmax UEs.
- NbIotCell.ulNonAnchPrbNum: Number of uplink non-anchor PRBs.
- NbIotCell.qQualMin: Minimum quality.
- NbIotCell.zzzTemporary18: Temporary field 18 (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.userLabel: User label for the cell.
- NbIotCell.zzzTemporary17: Temporary field 17 (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.zzzTemporary14: Temporary field 14 (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.zzzTemporary13: Temporary field 13 (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.zzzTemporary12: Temporary field 12 (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.zzzTemporary11: Temporary field 11 (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.hostingDigitalUnitRef: Reference to the hosting digital unit.
- NbIotCell.ceLevelNumber: Number of CE levels.
- NbIotCell.raNpuschSinrAdjustCe: NPUSCH SINR adjustment for RA (CE).
- NbIotCell.preambleIniRecTargetPower: Target power for preamble initial reception.
- NbIotCell.eutranCellRef: Reference to the E-UTRAN cell (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.alpha: Alpha value.
- NbIotCell.nbIotDynOverloadUlAnchThr: Uplink anchor overload threshold.
- NbIotCell.tTatDedicatedNbCe1: Dedicated TTI assignment time (CE1).
- NbIotCell.availabilityStatus: Availability status (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.qRxLevMin: Minimum received level.
- NbIotCell.tTatDedicatedNbCe0: Dedicated TTI assignment time (CE0).
- NbIotCell.nonPolledReleaseCfg: Configuration for non-polled release.
- NbIotCell.raiReleaseDelayTimer: RAI release delay timer.
- NbIotCell.msg3CqiReportEnabled: Flag indicating whether Msg3 CQI report is enabled.
- NbIotCell.raNprachSinrAdjustCe: NPRACH SINR adjustment for RA (CE).
- NbIotCell.pMax: Maximum power.
- NbIotCell.preschedUlGrantDelay: Prescheduled uplink grant delay.
- NbIotCell.nsssRrmConfigEnabled: Flag indicating whether NSSS RRM configuration is enabled.
- NbIotCell.zzzTemporary26: Temporary field 26 (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.zzzTemporary25: Temporary field 25 (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.zzzTemporary24: Temporary field 24 (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.microSleepTxPattern: Micro-sleep transmission pattern.
- NbIotCell.zzzTemporary23: Temporary field 23 (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.zzzTemporary22: Temporary field 22 (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.zzzTemporary21: Temporary field 21 (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.dataInactivityTimer: Data inactivity timer (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.abThreshTimeLow: Low threshold time for AB.
- NbIotCell.abIntensityObsrvPeriod: Observation period for AB intensity.
- NbIotCell.actualRsrpThreshold2: Actual second RSRP threshold.
- NbIotCell.logicalChannelSrProhibitTimer: Logical channel SR prohibit timer (likely empty).
- NbIotCell.msg5MeasReportEnabled: Flag indicating whether Msg5 measurement report is enabled.
- NbIotCell.abPresence: AB presence status.
- NbIotCell.tWaitForMmeCpRelocInd: Timer to wait for MME CP relocation indication.
- NbIotCell.actualRsrpThreshold1: Actual first RSRP threshold.
- NbIotCell.dlAnchPrbIndex: Downlink anchor PRB index.
- NbIotCell.abThreshRejectHigh: High threshold for AB rejection.
- NbIotCell.dvFactorForMsg5: DV factor for Msg5.
- NbIotCell.nprachAllocConfig: NPRACH allocation configuration.
- NbIotCell.retxBsrTimerDedicated: Retransmission timer for BSR (likely empty).
